@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ekyxer(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.08)) * wp.sin(0.83))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.abs(v2 + 0.98) + (tmp + 0.63 / v1 + 0.20)))
    v2 = 0.24
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v1 + 0.46) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.73)))
    tmp = v2
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.96) - v2) * ((tmp + 0.62 / v0 + 0.25) + (tmp + 0.15 / v1 + 0.57)))
    v0 = wp.exp(0.08)
    data[tid] = v0
